Op 22 november 1963 werd de Amerikaanse president John F. Kennedy doodgeschoten in Dallas, Texas.

en vice-president Johnson die de controle over het land moest nemen.


A recounting of the chaotic events that occurred at Dallas' Parkland Hospital on the day U.S. President John F. Kennedy was assassinated.
